@page "/"
@rendermode InteractiveServer

@* Web host shim. Home is the public landing page (no [Authorize] — the
   moved component renders distinct content for anonymous users). The
   QR-login panel is server-only (depends on QrLoginService + the
   /qrauthub SignalR hub) so we pass it via render fragment; MAUI's shim
   omits the slot. *@

<MudProviders />

<DropShot.UI.Components.Pages.Home>
    <AnonymousQrPanel>
        <QrLoginPanel />
    </AnonymousQrPanel>
</DropShot.UI.Components.Pages.Home>
